124
00:11:38,687 --> 00:11:41,854
His remains are scattered over there.

125
00:11:42,354 --> 00:11:43,229
Status?

126
00:11:45,687 --> 00:11:46,937
We've got five terrorists.

127
00:11:48,021 --> 00:11:49,520
- Inside or outside?
- Outside, thankfully.

128
00:11:49,521 --> 00:11:51,646
The parliament session was
adjourned 40 minutes ago.

129
